OL,3,CBee Network staff are voting on
OL,4,Cwhether to strike amid pay disputes
OL,6,FCommuters are facing "severe
OL,7,Fdisruption" if bus workers vote to
OL,8,Fstrike after rejecting a pay offer.
OL,10,FOver 2,000 Bee Network staff are
OL,11,Fvoting on whether to walkout after
OL,12,Frejecting pay offers from a number of
OL,13,Ftransport companies in Greater
OL,14,FManchester.
OL,16,FCompanies Stagecoach, Metroline
OL,17,FManchester and First Bus Rochdale
OL,18,Fcould see workers who are Unite
OL,19,Fmembers strike as early as mid-
OL,20,FSeptember, with the ballots set to
OL,21,Fclose on 4 September.
