OL,3,CBee Network staff are voting on
OL,4,Cwhether to strike amid pay disputes
OL,6,FAt Stagecoach, drivers based in
OL,7,FOldham, Stockport and Middleton depots
OL,8,Frejected a pay offer of 3.5%, while
OL,9,FStagecoach figures from last year
OL,10,Findicated an increased operating
OL,11,Fprofit of #51.1m.
OL,13,FMetroline Manchester workers rejected
OL,14,Fa similar offer, with workers
OL,15,Fbelieving "the offer doesn't address
OL,16,Fyears of low pay, especially in the
OL,17,Fcontext of the cost-of-living crisis."
