OL,6,FA ballot of Unite Union members
OL,7,Fworking at First Bus Rochdale
OL,8,Findicated that 95 per cent wanted to
OL,9,Freject a pay offer of six percent,
OL,10,Fstating it "doesn't address years of
OL,11,Flow pay, especially in the context of
OL,12,Fthe cost-of-living crisis."
OL,14,FUnite regional officer Colin Hayden
OL,15,Fsaid: "Should these strikes go ahead
OL,16,Fthey would bring Manchester's bus
OL,17,Fnetwork to a standstill.
