OL,3,CBee Network staff are voting on
OL,4,Cwhether to strike amid pay disputes
OL,6,F"We appreciate that residents who rely
OL,7,Fon these bus services will be
OL,8,Fdisappointed to hear of potential
OL,9,Faction, but it is entirely the fault
OL,10,Fof the employers. We urge them to come
OL,11,Fback to the table with improved offers
OL,12,Fto prevent what will be a highly
OL,13,Fdisruptive strike."
