OL,3,CBee Network staff are voting on
OL,4,Cwhether to strike amid pay disputes
OL,6,FA Transport for Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We're aware some
OL,8,Fof our Bee Network operators are
OL,9,Finvolved in ongoing pay negotiations
OL,10,Fand have been informed by them that
OL,11,Funion members are being balloted over
OL,12,Findustrial action. Bus operators are
OL,13,Fresponsible for the pay and conditions
OL,14,Fof their staff, and the specifics of
OL,15,Fany talks is a matter for them and the
OL,16,Frelevant trade union. Our priority is
OL,17,Fto keep Greater Manchester moving and
OL,18,Fwe are monitoring the situation
OL,19,Fclosely."
